                                    of information technology only, but has spread to all forms of businesses
                                    and service providers, private, public and individual. The economic
                                    scope and performance of the data centers, however, seem little discussed in
                                    the related literature. The rising cost of power supply, the crunch in storage
                                    space owing to high property prices, the difficulty of acquiring land for industrial
