                                    cost minimization and revenue forecasting for large data centers. Further,
                                    this paper offers factor analysis in order to identify the precise contribution
                                    of each factor input in the overall cost function. The operational management
                                    in large data centers has important outcomes in view of considerable
                                    externality associated with it.</p>
